'''[[Laguiole (takemmart)|Laguiole]]''' (nṭeq-it ''layul''), d [[tasiwelt n uẓar]] n tikemmarin [[Fransa|taṛumit]] n uẓi n [[Aubrac]] s [[takemmart n uyefki afraray |uyefki afraray n tfunast]]. Isem-is yekkad seg [[taddart]] n [[Laguiole (Aveyron)|Laguiole]] deg ugezdu n [[Aveyron (agezdu)|Aveyron]] di [[Fransa]].

Iẓuṛan n takemmart agi tettalin-d ar {{timiḍi wisXV}}, asmi imunaken n ugni n Aubrac, deg amnaḍ n ansay n takemmart adigan aqdim, sneflan asiweḍ (n iseksaten) n izegrawen uyefki dɣa bedden aɣraf ines. Tafarest-is tesɛa deg {{timiḍi wisXIX}} asfari d-ameqran aṭas, daɣen ula d-tisellat ines tesɛa. Tisellat nni ttwassebded ɣef ajmaɛ n tanzagt uɣzifen dɣa ɣef yiwet taɣara n ifarisen yecudden aṭas s wakal adigan : anezwu aweɛran, tiferdi tuzzigt n idurar, tifunasin n [[Aubrac (iri azegraw)|iri azegraw]]. 

Takemmart laguiole qrib tenger deg talemmast n {{timiḍi wisXX}}, ɣef ljal n atigen n uɣraf aɣlayen dɣa ilɣiten ad afen ixeddamen i uɣraf n takemmart deg ixxamen imensayen "[[buron]]". Yuɣaled, seg iseggwasen 1960, s tallalt n infarasen idiganen, yebɣan ad snernin tukkest n timiḍiwin yezwiren. Tafarest tesniled seg iseggwasen 1980 ɣer taɣara d [[takemmart n ujmaɛ|tikemmarin n ujmaɛ]] dɣa gweḍen-d seg taggara n iseggwasen 1990 ar tasmekta talemmast yetṛuḥun gar 700 d {{unité|750|iṭunen}} n laguiole yenzan yal aseggwas.

Tasiwelt agi yettwaḥerzen sɣur  [[Ticreḍt n taɣara|ticraḍ]] AOC seg useggwas [[1961]] d AOP seg [[2008]]. Tafarest n uyefki, tafarest d umesel n [[takemmart|tikemmarin]] ilaq ad yetwexdem deg taɣzut tamaḍlarant n aẓi agmawi n Aubrac i bεuẓẓelen ɣef 73 timdinin n igezda n [[Aveyron (agezdu)|Aveyron]], n [[Cantal (agezdu)|Cantal]] dɣa n [[Lozère (agezdu)|Lozère]].


